sources.title: Shockproof (restored, with intro and outro) (1949, film noir, imdb score: 6.5)
sources.description: Shockproof is a 1949 American crime film noir directed by Douglas Sirk and starring Patricia Knight and Cornel Wilde. Wilde and Knight were husband and wife during filming. They divorced in 1951.
